data.description: This spacious and tastefully updated 4 BR/3 bath ranch is picture perfect and located in the desirable Kings Grant neighborhood. Being offered turn key! Fully furnished!Enter through your petty foyer, to the living room which has French doors to the 4 season sunroom, with multiple sliders to the patio and private back yard. There is a large formal dining room with bow windows, a cozy offic and sunny kitchen. First floor laundry, a primary bedroom with private bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms and bath plus a 2nd staircase to your finished loft family room, beautiful bedroom with 2 walk in closets and full bath. New central A/C, with splits on the 2nd floor bonus area. Zoned FHW gas heat, oversized 2 car garage, full basement, attic area above the garage and nice corner lot! Walk to tennis, baseball, the bay, beach and all that the quaint village of Cotuit offers. Shows like a model home, tastefully furnished and finished. Just bring your phone and suitcase!All buyers and their representatives are encouraged to verify all info.
